docs_Docs_explanationDescription: Complete all steps to get your first customer!
docs_ProfilePhoto_explanationDescription: Your profile photo helps people recognize you
docs_ProfilePhoto_tip1: 1. Face the camera directly with your eyes and mouth clearly visible.
docs_ProfilePhoto_tip2: 2. Make sure the photo is well lit, free of glare, and in focus.
docs_ProfilePhoto_tip3: 3. No photos of a photo, filters or alterations.
docs_DriversLicense_explanationTitle: Take a photo of your driver’s license
docs_DriversLicense_explanationDescripti: Make sure your driver’s license is not expired and avoid using your flash to prevent glare
docs_VehicleInsurance_explanationTitle: Take a photo of your vehicle insurance
docs_VehicleInsurance_explanationDescrip: Make sure your name, VIN, insurance company and expiration date are clear and readable. If your name is not listed on your insurance card, upload a copy of the Declaration Page instead that shows your name on the policy
docs_VehicleRegistration_explanationTitl: Take a photo of your vehicle registration
docs_VehicleRegistration_explanationDesc: Make sure your vehicle’s make, model, year, license plate. VIN, and expiration are clear and readable
docs_BackgroundCheck_explanationDescript: SNN is needed for payments and to run your background check
docs_BackgroundCheck_agreement1: Your personal information is protected and secure
docs_BackgroundCheck_agreement2: No credit check needed - your credit won’t be affected
docs_VehicleInspection_explanationDescri:
Your city and ShuttleX require that your vehicle be inspected to help maintain driver and rider safety

It’s a simple check to make sure everything is on working order
